Quasar:




"I'm not lost!" Quasar snapped at Venus. "I was watching out for the 
rest of Megatron's troops when they went back to base, now I'm going. 
If you want something, just say it!"

She was a little uneased about this bot. She turned her shoulder from 
her to walk the rest of the way up the mountain.

with her.

that its 
> cold and youre lost. Come with me back to my ship. Right now." She 
had 
> finally lost patience with the girl, and her palms began to emit a 
blue glow 
> to them. They were charged, and ready to send a bolt of energon at 
the girl.
